rent leadership structure, exiting executives, and doubling down on his Zac=
 Posen experiment. (Even Posen, himself, might not be safe=E2=80=A6)

Plus, below the fold: Peter Hamby offers a bracing prescription for the Dem=
ocrats=E2=80=99 dark night of the soul. John Ourand teams up with LightShed=
=E2=80=99s Rich Greenfield to assess how the sports media business could tr=
ansform under Trump. And Scott Mendelson previews the pre-Thanksgiving box =
office trifecta of Gladiator II, Wicked: Part One, and Moana 2.

